					<lb xml:id="p3z2"/>L.
					<pb/>
					<lb xml:id="p4z1"/>Reverendo viro, sapientia doctrina
					<lb xml:id="p4z2"/>pietate praestanti, domino Heinricho Bullingero,
					<lb xml:id="p4z3"/>ecclesiae Tigurinae pastori fidelissimo,
					<lb xml:id="p4z4"/>domino ac facitori suo tanquam patri colendissimo.
					<lb xml:id="p4z5"/>Z&#252;rich.
